value.value: Adult brain-intrinsic neuron with its soma in the brain, anterior to the antennal mechanosensory and motor center (Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024). It belongs to the ALl1_ventral hemilineage (Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024). It has postsynapses in the ipsilateral antennal mechanosensory and motor center, the ipsilateral posterior ventrolateral protocerebrum and the saddle (Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024). It has presynapses in the ipsilateral posterior ventrolateral protocerebrum, the ipsilateral antennal mechanosensory and motor center and the saddle (Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024). Its predicted neurotransmitter is acetylcholine (Eckstein et al., 2024). There are approximately 4 of these cells per organism (Schlegel et al., 2024; Dorkenwald et al., 2024).
